Silicon Labs Si32 HAL

Origin:
   Silicon Labs Precision32
   https://www.silabs.com/developers/precision32-32-bit-microcontroller-development-suite

Version:
   v1.1.2

Purpose:
   Add support for Silicon Labs SiM3U1xx SoCs

Description:
   This code component is used to add Zephyr support for Silicon Labs SiM3U1xx SoCs.
   To speed up the development process it is based on the Silicon Labs HAL.

   The following folder is partially imported: si32Hal

   That SDK has a proprietary license, but we do have permission to relicense
   it to ZLIB. See [0] or [1] for more information.

Dependencies:
   This source code depends on headers and sources from Zephyr:
   modules/hal/cmsis

URL:
   https://www.silabs.com/developers/precision32-32-bit-microcontroller-development-suite

Maintained-by:
   External

