How to update
+++++++++++++

This was tested with p7zip 17.04.

  * Download precision32-development-environment-offline.exe
  * run `./scripts/extract_hal /path/to/downloaded-file`
  * The extracted HAL will be in `$CWD/tmp`
  * run `./scripts/copy_hal`
  * The HAL with be copied to si32HAL with the license headers patched

